---
title: Moroccan Beef Meatballs with Couscous & Flaked Almonds
description: Roll up for our latest take on meatballs – a Moroccan version flavoured with ras el hanout! This exotic spice blend's name means 'top of the shop', as it was considered the best spice mix a merchant had to offer. It gives these beef meatballs an abundance of flavour and we've added couscous studded with baby spinach and mint to round out the meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d09c68567dfb3000f08b165-d4bdffc3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/moroccan-beef-meatballs-5d09c68567dfb3000f08b165-5eb8d129.pdf
